🚨 New episode schedule ‼️
We have been working hard every day to find more ways to add value to your life and help you become the best version of yourself!

I’m happy to announce there is now 4 new episodes every week! The newest addition to the weekly lineup is the “Win in Parenting” episodes where I either bring on a guest or directly answer questions asked from the audience about parenting advice.

This is one of the rare podcasts that puts out this many episodes every week! 

Watch or listen only on the Patreon app. Get full access for free for 7 days. No commitment. Cancel anytime.
